(define/contract (count-tested-devices batteryPercentages)
  (-> (listof exact-integer?) exact-integer?)
  
  ; Helper function to decrement the battery percentages of devices
  ; from index start to the end of the list
  (define (decrement-batteries lst start)
    (if (null? lst)
        '()
        (cons (if (< start 0)
                  (car lst)
                  (max 0 (- (car lst) 1)))
              (decrement-batteries (cdr lst) (- start 1)))))

  ; Main function logic
  (let loop ([batteries batteryPercentages]
             [index 0]
             [count 0])
    (cond
      [(null? batteries) count] ; When all devices have been checked
      [(> (car batteries) 0)
       ; Test the device and decrement the rest
       (loop (decrement-batteries batteries 0)
             (+ index 1)
             (+ count 1))]
      [else
       ; Move to the next device without testing
       (loop (cdr batteries)
             (+ index 1)
             count)])))
